<p><span style="float:left; weight: semibold; margin-left:5px; margin-top:12px; color: black; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0px 10px;"><br />
Last Edited 1:22PM OWST by Some Dude Hitting Golf Balls On The Moon<br /></span></p>
<p><span style="float:right; margin-left:5px; margin-top:6px; color: purple; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0px 10px;"><br />
[<strong>EDIT</strong>] [<strong>HISTORY</strong>] |[<strong>[COMMENTS(35)]</strong>]<br /></span></p>
<div style="clear:both; height: 0px; font-size: 1px"></div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Would&nbsp;You&nbsp;Like&nbsp;To&nbsp;Learn&nbsp;More?</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">eroM&nbsp;nraeL&nbsp;oT&nbsp;ekiL&nbsp;uoY&nbsp;dluoW</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content"><script type="text/javascript" src="http://d3g0gp89917ko0.cloudfront.net/v--3e3a6f7dbcc9/common--javascript/yahooui/tabview-min.js">
</script>
<div id="wiki-tabview-f0af228d5ac3cb36099d4717c31b233a" class="yui-navset">
<ul class="yui-nav">
<li class="selected"><a href="javascript:;"><em>Information</em></a></li>
<li><a href="javascript:;"><em>Templates</em></a></li>
</ul>
<div class="yui-content">
<div id="wiki-tab-0-0">
<p>In the next tab are the web page templates for Oneiroi West &quot;sites&quot;. You can create your own if you can't find the website you're trying to mimic here, or you can code something more representative.</p>
<p>In the sense that the internet is connected computers, the Oneiroi net is connected minds. The representations aren't to be taken at face value; what you see here is the singular mind making sense of the troves of abstract information collected upon waking.</p>
</div>
